  <source>Eurofarma Laboratorios S.A.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study's objective is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of two formulations for the
      prophylactic treatment of diarrhea in subjects using antibiotics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
